Build openttd-ubports (in a libertine container)
`./configure CFLAGS='-D__UBPORTS__' CXXFLAGS='-D__UBPORTS__' --prefix=$PWD/install`
`make -j4`
`make install`

Copy openttd.apparmor, openttd.desktop and manifest.json.in into the bin folder
Manually set the CLICK_ARCH in manifest.json.in and change it to manifest.json
Run `click build .` (I did this outside of the container)
`pkcon install-local --allow-untrusted openttd.abmyii_20200708_armhf.click`
